window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One moment in time changed the course of our lives....</b></p> <p><i>For more than two decades, I vow to find her.</i></p> <p>I'm locked up. Full of rage. Obsessed with remembering every detail about her.</p> <p>When I get out, I scour the Earth. Relentlessly. Mercilessly.</p> <p>I know she's out there. I can still feel her, my firefly glowing in the dark.</p> <p><b>I'll never stop until she's back in my arms.</b></p> <p><b><i>Relentless Hunter</i></b><b> is the 10th and final jaw-dropping installment of the Mafia Wars series and part of the O’Malley saga. It's a second chance dark mafia romance, interconnecting stand-alone, and guaranteed to have an HEA.</b></p>"; 
